Jerry Lei

Project description: The project is a two player text-based hangman.

User interface: There will be a client/server connection between two players. One of the players will be the person who puts up the word to guess along with a clue. The second player will guess characters or a word to match the word the first player puts up.


Topics used:
 -networking
 -processes
 -signals
 -text input

Potential:
 -chat
 -more than 2 players, taking turns on guessing word
  
Timeline:
 -Design
 -Production of hangman 
 -Put into network
 -Testing
 